1
00:01:30,700 --> 00:01:34,983
(Gen Z)

2
00:01:35,711 --> 00:01:38,202
(Episode 12)

3
00:01:40,859 --> 00:01:42,340
Take everything in moderation.

4
00:01:43,340 --> 00:01:44,739
This is my reward for you.

5
00:01:44,948 --> 00:01:45,747
-Here.
-Alright.

6
00:01:45,819 --> 00:01:46,900
If so,

7
00:01:47,260 --> 00:01:48,099
I'll take the entire pot.

8
00:01:48,260 --> 00:01:49,539
I don't want to share it with you.

9
00:01:54,459 --> 00:01:55,262
Just pour a little for me.

10
00:01:55,419 --> 00:01:56,580
-Come on.
-Take everything in moderation.

11
00:01:56,580 --> 00:01:57,620
You said so yourself.

12
00:01:59,380 --> 00:02:00,188
-Just a little more.
-Stop drinking.

13
00:02:00,300 --> 00:02:01,739
-Just a little more.
-Stop drinking. Have some food.

14
00:02:01,805 --> 00:02:02,609
Alright.

15
00:02:02,739 --> 00:02:03,940
Your mouth is so oily.

16
00:02:03,940 --> 00:02:05,020
Wipe your mouth.

17
00:02:05,219 --> 00:02:06,539
Stop drinking.

18
00:02:08,658 --> 00:02:10,219
Wait. What are you doing?

19
00:02:10,220 --> 00:02:11,119
Hey.

20
00:02:11,340 --> 00:02:12,299
There's not much left.

21
00:02:12,860 --> 00:02:14,060
-Just a little.
-Just a little?

22
00:02:14,260 --> 00:02:15,465
-Yeah.
-Just a little, okay?

23
00:02:15,780 --> 00:02:17,099
Only a little.

24
00:02:17,140 --> 00:02:17,940
That's enough.

25
00:02:17,954 --> 00:02:19,355
That's too much.

26
00:02:21,299 --> 00:02:22,500
Cheers.

27
00:02:22,860 --> 00:02:23,939
You don't understand, right?

28
00:02:24,579 --> 00:02:26,299
Cheers is what they say in English.

29
00:02:27,500 --> 00:02:28,433
Cheers.

30
00:02:33,459 --> 00:02:34,739
How much did you drink?

31
00:02:35,060 --> 00:02:36,340
How did you get so drunk?

32
00:02:37,179 --> 00:02:39,060
I'll make some hangover soup for you.

33
00:03:17,939 --> 00:03:18,770
Here.

34
00:03:19,739 --> 00:03:20,620
Drink this.

35
00:03:27,019 --> 00:03:29,019
Don't you know how much liquor

36
00:03:29,860 --> 00:03:30,860
you can drink?

37
00:03:31,739 --> 00:03:33,659
I'm teaching students in accordance

38
00:03:34,420 --> 00:03:35,739
with their aptitude.

39
00:03:37,220 --> 00:03:40,379
First, I lure her in with desire.

40
00:03:41,019 --> 00:03:44,140
After that, I'll bring her to
the righteous path.

41
00:03:47,860 --> 00:03:49,659
Tou Tou is a promising child.

42
00:03:50,860 --> 00:03:52,060
It's just that it's difficult

43
00:03:52,060 --> 00:03:53,819
to be her teacher.

44
00:03:54,420 --> 00:03:55,420
Look at me.

45
00:03:56,060 --> 00:03:57,420
I'm giving everything I got

46
00:03:58,060 --> 00:04:00,060
to realise Master's dream.

47
00:04:00,500 --> 00:04:02,140
I've never seen you put this much effort

48
00:04:02,140 --> 00:04:03,220
in teaching Tian Zhen.

49
00:04:03,379 --> 00:04:04,220
It's because I know

50
00:04:04,220 --> 00:04:06,060
Tian Zhen

51
00:04:06,060 --> 00:04:07,459
belongs here.

52
00:04:10,379 --> 00:04:11,780
He can't run away.

53
00:04:15,220 --> 00:04:16,380
But Tou Tou?

54
00:04:17,299 --> 00:04:18,660
She might run away

55
00:04:18,660 --> 00:04:19,859
if we take our eyes off her.

56
00:04:20,578 --> 00:04:21,418
I think

57
00:04:21,419 --> 00:04:23,419
you're sure that I won't run away.

58
00:04:23,660 --> 00:04:25,060
That's why you make
endless demands of me.

59
00:04:26,500 --> 00:04:28,179
Dear, that sounds unfair to me.

60
00:04:29,299 --> 00:04:30,220
Unfair?

61
00:04:30,780 --> 00:04:32,060
Was I wrong?

62
00:04:34,500 --> 00:04:35,579
You put so much effort

63
00:04:36,940 --> 00:04:38,259
in treating outsiders.

64
00:04:38,259 --> 00:04:39,419
What about your family?

65
00:04:42,780 --> 00:04:43,579
This is

66
00:04:44,299 --> 00:04:46,019
a common problem among humans.

67
00:04:46,660 --> 00:04:47,660
We always show outsiders

68
00:04:48,019 --> 00:04:50,019
our best side

69
00:04:50,419 --> 00:04:52,979
and show our family members
our worst side.

70
00:04:58,419 --> 00:04:59,979
Don't think

71
00:04:59,979 --> 00:05:01,859
that I invited Tou Tou to drink with me

72
00:05:01,859 --> 00:05:03,660
so that I could transform her.

73
00:05:04,419 --> 00:05:06,699
I was cleaning up the mess
your son had made.

74
00:05:07,380 --> 00:05:08,419
If so, why didn't you let him

75
00:05:08,660 --> 00:05:10,060
treat the girl during the forum?

76
00:05:12,780 --> 00:05:14,380
So, you were waiting
to say that all along?

77
00:05:16,500 --> 00:05:17,739
I was wondering

78
00:05:17,739 --> 00:05:19,060
why everything

79
00:05:19,060 --> 00:05:20,220
wasn't proceeding smoothly lately.

80
00:05:20,620 --> 00:05:22,220
Your son wasn't ready yet.

81
00:05:23,060 --> 00:05:24,579
If you don't let him give it a try,

82
00:05:24,859 --> 00:05:26,940
he'll never be ready.

83
00:05:28,060 --> 00:05:29,019
Both you

84
00:05:29,739 --> 00:05:31,019
and Uncle were around.

85
00:05:33,060 --> 00:05:35,500
And, he wanted to send Tian Zhen
to give the girl a diagnosis.

86
00:05:35,500 --> 00:05:37,780
He wanted to see how capable
Tian Zhen was.

87
00:05:38,060 --> 00:05:40,620
You only look on the bright side.

88
00:05:41,459 --> 00:05:42,780
What if your son

89
00:05:43,419 --> 00:05:45,139
made things worse?

90
00:05:45,739 --> 00:05:46,859
If Tou Tou made things worse,

91
00:05:47,139 --> 00:05:49,419
everyone could at least
come to terms with it.

92
00:05:49,739 --> 00:05:50,940
I could back her up.

93
00:05:51,940 --> 00:05:52,940
But if I send your son there

94
00:05:53,419 --> 00:05:54,419
and back him up,

95
00:05:54,859 --> 00:05:56,739
the Song family

96
00:05:56,739 --> 00:05:58,019
will be embarrassed.

97
00:05:59,780 --> 00:06:01,419
I didn't send your son there

98
00:06:01,780 --> 00:06:04,060
in order to protect him.

99
00:06:04,900 --> 00:06:05,859
Goodness.

100
00:06:07,139 --> 00:06:08,459
This concerns the girl's life, you know?

101
00:06:09,139 --> 00:06:10,459
Listen.

102
00:06:11,220 --> 00:06:13,419
I'll tell you this.

103
00:06:14,459 --> 00:06:16,780
Although Tou Tou is boorish,

104
00:06:17,100 --> 00:06:18,459
she's talented.

105
00:06:18,940 --> 00:06:20,459
She's talented

106
00:06:20,500 --> 00:06:22,500
and she's meant to take this path.

107
00:06:23,179 --> 00:06:24,780
She might be distracted

108
00:06:24,780 --> 00:06:26,739
during our lessons,

109
00:06:28,060 --> 00:06:30,060
however, she has a delicate heart.

110
00:06:30,060 --> 00:06:32,100
Her eyes and ears were open
and receptive.

111
00:06:33,500 --> 00:06:34,620
She remembered everything

112
00:06:34,620 --> 00:06:36,380
I said and taught.

113
00:06:36,620 --> 00:06:38,019
Not only did she observe what I taught,

114
00:06:39,060 --> 00:06:39,856
but she could also apply them.

115
00:06:40,620 --> 00:06:41,820
She observed that Mr Zheng's daughter

116
00:06:41,820 --> 00:06:43,620
had eczema.

117
00:06:44,179 --> 00:06:45,019
When your son was there,

118
00:06:45,620 --> 00:06:46,441
he only said

119
00:06:46,900 --> 00:06:47,768
that she had a fever.

120
00:06:48,739 --> 00:06:50,179
He may be able to cure her fever,

121
00:06:50,179 --> 00:06:51,739
but he'll never think of

122
00:06:51,940 --> 00:06:53,820
making egg yolk oil on the scene

123
00:06:53,820 --> 00:06:54,660
and letting the girl apply it.

124
00:06:55,859 --> 00:06:56,739
Do you think he'll think of that?

125
00:06:57,220 --> 00:06:58,500
He'll never think of that.

126
00:06:59,340 --> 00:07:00,940
The people there might have

127
00:07:00,940 --> 00:07:02,820
a doctorate or a Master's degree,

128
00:07:02,859 --> 00:07:03,780
but none of them

129
00:07:03,780 --> 00:07:05,859
can do any better than Tou Tou.

130
00:07:07,900 --> 00:07:08,900
You're excited and proud

131
00:07:08,900 --> 00:07:10,299
when you talk about Sun Tou Tou.

132
00:07:13,380 --> 00:07:14,259
You feel like throwing up again?

133
00:07:16,900 --> 00:07:17,753
I'll go to the toilet.

134
00:07:28,019 --> 00:07:29,179
Li Quan applied for leave again?

135
00:07:29,340 --> 00:07:31,459
Yes, this is already the second time
this month.

136
00:07:31,459 --> 00:07:32,299
And, he applied for leave once

137
00:07:32,299 --> 00:07:33,179
during our weekend lesson.

138
00:07:34,900 --> 00:07:35,748
Tian Zhen,

139
00:07:36,780 --> 00:07:38,060
did you know that Li Quan
applied for leave?

140
00:07:38,620 --> 00:07:39,500
I know that.

141
00:07:40,940 --> 00:07:41,842
Where did he go?

142
00:07:42,340 --> 00:07:43,225
He...

143
00:07:43,859 --> 00:07:44,780
He's doing a part-time job.

144
00:07:45,900 --> 00:07:46,820
A part-time job?

145
00:07:49,459 --> 00:07:50,340
What does that mean?

146
00:07:52,179 --> 00:07:53,005
He's doing foot massages.

147
00:07:53,116 --> 00:07:53,998
Dr Song,

148
00:07:54,179 --> 00:07:55,459
someone left their belongings
in the storeroom.

149
00:07:55,459 --> 00:07:56,317
Come and take a look.

150
00:08:04,859 --> 00:08:05,859
Call Zhao Li Quan.

151
00:08:06,500 --> 00:08:07,419
Tell him to pack his belongings.

152
00:08:08,500 --> 00:08:09,940
How could he keep them here?

153
00:08:11,900 --> 00:08:13,179
This is a medical centre, not a hotel.

154
00:08:14,739 --> 00:08:16,660
The medicine we use
will be consumed by the patients.

155
00:08:19,019 --> 00:08:21,179
Where will he stay then?

156
00:08:21,179 --> 00:08:22,060
Take his things out.

157
00:08:22,060 --> 00:08:23,019
How is that my business?

158
00:08:26,179 --> 00:08:27,033
Tian Zhen,

159
00:08:27,500 --> 00:08:29,380
is Li Quan facing any difficulties?

160
00:08:30,380 --> 00:08:33,019
I lent him my dorm last time.

161
00:08:33,220 --> 00:08:34,579
But the dorm had tight security.

162
00:08:34,579 --> 00:08:36,499
I told him to stay here
for the time being.

163
00:08:36,499 --> 00:08:38,220
I think he's going to rent a unit soon.

164
00:08:38,220 --> 00:08:39,059
That's why he applied for leave

165
00:08:39,059 --> 00:08:40,900
in order to work outside.

166
00:08:41,619 --> 00:08:42,939
He should find a job

167
00:08:42,939 --> 00:08:45,019
with stable income.

168
00:08:45,780 --> 00:08:47,059
He can come and learn

169
00:08:47,220 --> 00:08:48,139
when he has time.

170
00:08:49,059 --> 00:08:51,300
If so, you can just give him a job.

171
00:08:52,019 --> 00:08:53,499
Just make him a pharmaceutical worker.

172
00:08:53,740 --> 00:08:55,180
He can prepare prescriptions.

173
00:08:55,579 --> 00:08:56,860
He can study at the same time.

174
00:08:56,860 --> 00:08:57,900
And, he'll make some money too.

175
00:08:57,900 --> 00:08:58,860
Isn't that the best of both worlds?

176
00:09:00,660 --> 00:09:03,100
Zhao Li Quan will be
a doctor in the future.

177
00:09:04,579 --> 00:09:07,499
He can't just steal other people's jobs.

178
00:09:07,499 --> 00:09:08,340
Go and ask him.

179
00:09:09,619 --> 00:09:10,499
It's either he continues his study

180
00:09:11,059 --> 00:09:11,946
or works outside.

181
00:09:12,860 --> 00:09:14,619
You're discriminating against him here.

182
00:09:15,220 --> 00:09:17,220
Why can Peng Shi Yan work
while studying then?

183
00:09:17,259 --> 00:09:18,420
Why can't Zhao Li Quan do the same?

184
00:09:19,499 --> 00:09:21,340
Peng Shi Yan

185
00:09:21,340 --> 00:09:23,740
doesn't make a living
as a TCM practitioner.

186
00:09:24,180 --> 00:09:26,340
TCM is Zhao Li Quan's livelihood.

187
00:09:26,619 --> 00:09:27,740
He needs medical skills

188
00:09:27,740 --> 00:09:29,619
to make a living, understood?

189
00:09:31,139 --> 00:09:32,540
I think Tian Zhen's suggestion

190
00:09:33,740 --> 00:09:35,259
is worth considering.

191
00:09:35,259 --> 00:09:36,860
It might work.

192
00:09:37,540 --> 00:09:38,660
If Li Quan is around,

193
00:09:39,300 --> 00:09:40,379
at least he can help us out

194
00:09:40,379 --> 00:09:42,780
when we're busy preparing prescriptions.

195
00:09:43,300 --> 00:09:44,740
He's familiar with herbs and medicine.

196
00:09:45,180 --> 00:09:46,499
And, he was professionally trained
in this field.

197
00:09:47,819 --> 00:09:49,540
He can prepare prescriptions

198
00:09:49,619 --> 00:09:50,699
when we give diagnoses.

199
00:09:51,059 --> 00:09:52,579
He can study with the other classmates

200
00:09:52,699 --> 00:09:53,819
when there's a class.

201
00:09:53,939 --> 00:09:55,499
This is our place after all.

202
00:09:56,139 --> 00:09:58,379
We can pay him according to
a part-timer's rate.

203
00:09:58,379 --> 00:09:59,340
What do you think?

204
00:09:59,939 --> 00:10:01,619
Niece-in-law already said so much.

205
00:10:01,619 --> 00:10:02,459
Nephew,

206
00:10:02,459 --> 00:10:04,259
why don't you consider it?

207
00:10:06,300 --> 00:10:07,819
Why are you calling me Nephew again?

208
00:10:08,699 --> 00:10:11,499
Because it's time for me
to show my authority as your senior.

209
00:10:19,499 --> 00:10:21,340
I know you guys are
doing this for his sake.

210
00:10:22,180 --> 00:10:24,420
But the thing is,

211
00:10:24,420 --> 00:10:25,459
Zhao Li Quan

212
00:10:25,619 --> 00:10:28,059
must understand what he truly desires.

213
00:10:28,059 --> 00:10:29,499
That's the main thing.

214
00:10:29,716 --> 00:10:30,567
That's it for now.

215
00:10:32,540 --> 00:10:33,364
Call him.

216
00:10:34,300 --> 00:10:35,139
He can't stay here.

217
00:10:41,699 --> 00:10:42,499
So, does that mean

218
00:10:42,499 --> 00:10:43,459
your father has agreed to it?

219
00:10:45,379 --> 00:10:46,420
Your seniority does work wonders.

220
00:10:58,860 --> 00:10:59,780
You've been applying for leave

221
00:10:59,780 --> 00:11:00,939
just to work here?

222
00:11:03,259 --> 00:11:04,104
Quit the job.

223
00:11:04,619 --> 00:11:06,459
You're a postgraduate student
from a decent medical academy.

224
00:11:06,459 --> 00:11:08,619
Why are you working
in a massage parlour?

225
00:11:08,980 --> 00:11:10,259
I'll get you a decent job.

226
00:11:10,259 --> 00:11:11,180
-Come with me.
-Tian Zhen.

227
00:11:14,699 --> 00:11:15,592
Thank you.

228
00:11:16,499 --> 00:11:17,860
You always helped me out.

229
00:11:17,860 --> 00:11:19,059
I feel pretty bad about it.

230
00:11:19,619 --> 00:11:20,499
I appreciate your kindness,

231
00:11:20,499 --> 00:11:21,379
but I'm doing great here.

232
00:11:21,379 --> 00:11:22,202
Doing great?

233
00:11:22,579 --> 00:11:23,379
You apply for leave during the day.

234
00:11:23,379 --> 00:11:24,699
You don't even attend
our lessons on the weekend.

235
00:11:24,980 --> 00:11:26,860
My father was unhappy that
you applied for leave today.

236
00:11:27,180 --> 00:11:28,059
Besides, if you work at night,

237
00:11:28,059 --> 00:11:29,900
you won't have the energy to
attend class on the second day.

238
00:11:30,180 --> 00:11:31,740
If there's a situation in your family,

239
00:11:31,740 --> 00:11:32,699
-you can tell me.
-Tian Zhen.

240
00:11:32,699 --> 00:11:33,539
I can help you out.

241
00:11:37,699 --> 00:11:39,379
I know you're doing it for my sake.

242
00:11:40,459 --> 00:11:42,980
But it's not like I can accept your help

243
00:11:43,459 --> 00:11:46,300
every time without any pressure.

244
00:11:49,819 --> 00:11:51,300
I'm a man too. I have my dignity.

245
00:11:51,499 --> 00:11:52,780
You said this yourself.

246
00:11:52,780 --> 00:11:54,379
You said you would find a mentor
in the apprentice class

247
00:11:54,379 --> 00:11:55,699
and ask them to take you
under their wing.

248
00:11:55,699 --> 00:11:56,860
How could you learn from them

249
00:11:56,860 --> 00:11:57,660
when you're doing this?

250
00:11:59,699 --> 00:12:00,860
I do want to get a mentor

251
00:12:00,860 --> 00:12:02,059
and learn under them.

252
00:12:03,259 --> 00:12:05,379
However, I need to survive first.

253
00:12:06,420 --> 00:12:07,420
You saw this yourself.

254
00:12:08,059 --> 00:12:09,420
I've always been working outside.

255
00:12:10,499 --> 00:12:11,619
It was different when I was in college.

256
00:12:11,619 --> 00:12:12,540
Back then, I was just
providing for myself.

257
00:12:12,540 --> 00:12:13,420
I didn't need to provide for my family.

258
00:12:13,540 --> 00:12:14,340
Now, it's different.

259
00:12:14,340 --> 00:12:15,939
Now, I have to make money
and provide for my family.

260
00:12:17,980 --> 00:12:19,340
Forget it. Let's drop the topic.

261
00:12:19,340 --> 00:12:20,300
You won't understand anyway.

262
00:12:21,540 --> 00:12:23,459
Your starting point is the endpoint
I've been trying to achieve.

263
00:12:23,499 --> 00:12:24,740
Wait. What did you say?

264
00:12:24,740 --> 00:12:26,180
-Wait.
-This is...

265
00:12:26,300 --> 00:12:28,300
What are you guys saying?

266
00:12:29,420 --> 00:12:30,740
You guys are going off-topic here.

267
00:12:30,740 --> 00:12:32,019
It's way off-topic.

268
00:12:33,059 --> 00:12:35,939
Is it that complicated?

269
00:12:36,300 --> 00:12:37,579
Do you wish to find

270
00:12:37,939 --> 00:12:39,180
a way for you to study

271
00:12:39,180 --> 00:12:40,740
and make money at the same time?

272
00:12:40,980 --> 00:12:42,300
Right now, there's such a deal.

273
00:12:42,900 --> 00:12:44,499
It can satisfy your need to study

274
00:12:44,619 --> 00:12:46,300
and help you make money too.
Do you want it or not?

275
00:12:46,300 --> 00:12:47,220
Why are you here?

276
00:12:47,420 --> 00:12:48,619
Why the heck are you here?

277
00:12:49,059 --> 00:12:50,220
Didn't you come here

278
00:12:50,220 --> 00:12:51,619
