00:35:16,299 --> 00:35:17,379
I can get you

843
00:35:17,379 --> 00:35:18,539
the toy you want.

844
00:35:18,539 --> 00:35:19,460
It's hard to say.

845
00:35:19,779 --> 00:35:20,779
We can do it too.

846
00:35:21,180 --> 00:35:21,980
What are you

847
00:35:21,980 --> 00:35:22,819
saying?

848
00:35:23,740 --> 00:35:24,900
-You want to play?
-Yeah.

849
00:35:24,900 --> 00:35:25,740
I'm good at this. Come.

850
00:35:25,740 --> 00:35:26,900
It's impossible.

851
00:35:26,900 --> 00:35:28,180
Listen, I'll get it on my first try.

852
00:35:28,180 --> 00:35:29,460
You're just wasting your money.

853
00:35:29,460 --> 00:35:30,500
That's impossible. Look.

854
00:35:32,460 --> 00:35:33,500
Let me show you.

855
00:35:42,220 --> 00:35:43,020
Senior,

856
00:35:43,500 --> 00:35:45,460
I don't think I can do that.

857
00:35:46,260 --> 00:35:47,940
(You own many companies
in the tertiary industry.)

858
00:35:48,500 --> 00:35:50,779
Is it that hard for me
to get a classroom?

859
00:35:50,980 --> 00:35:51,986
That's not the hard part.

860
00:35:52,500 --> 00:35:54,579
The hard part is to pacify the people.

861
00:35:55,299 --> 00:35:56,779
You see, if I'm giving you
what you want now,

862
00:35:57,099 --> 00:35:58,034
what should I do

863
00:35:58,539 --> 00:35:59,539
when other people ask me
for the same thing?

864
00:36:00,139 --> 00:36:01,660
If I don't give it to them,
I'll be biased.

865
00:36:01,980 --> 00:36:03,420
(You and I are from the same sect.)

866
00:36:03,579 --> 00:36:04,900
(Just one report letter)

867
00:36:05,020 --> 00:36:06,180
(is enough to land me in trouble.)

868
00:36:06,779 --> 00:36:08,180
I thought you promised

869
00:36:08,220 --> 00:36:09,260
Fellow Zhang

870
00:36:09,460 --> 00:36:11,020
that your academy would help us out

871
00:36:11,020 --> 00:36:12,379
if we were in trouble?

872
00:36:12,420 --> 00:36:14,500
Now, the apprentice class
is in a pickle here.

873
00:36:14,500 --> 00:36:15,660
How do you plan to resolve the issue?

874
00:36:17,621 --> 00:36:18,555
Me?

875
00:36:20,980 --> 00:36:22,299
At most, I can hold one,

876
00:36:22,299 --> 00:36:23,156
two,

877
00:36:23,589 --> 00:36:24,589
or even three seminars for you.

878
00:36:25,059 --> 00:36:27,339
(But now, you're asking me
for a classroom.)

879
00:36:27,579 --> 00:36:29,020
And, you'll be using it
for quite a few years.

880
00:36:29,020 --> 00:36:30,460
The thing is,
you're not paying rent for it.

881
00:36:31,180 --> 00:36:32,940
How can I explain myself
to the higher-ups?

882
00:36:35,900 --> 00:36:36,900
What about this?

883
00:36:37,452 --> 00:36:38,932
For the sake of your apprentice class,

884
00:36:39,500 --> 00:36:42,539
I'll sacrifice my career.

885
00:36:43,139 --> 00:36:44,740
I'll resign

886
00:36:45,180 --> 00:36:46,579
(and be the class teacher)

887
00:36:46,819 --> 00:36:48,099
(for the apprentice class.)

888
00:36:48,260 --> 00:36:51,660
I'll be thick-skinned and go out
to ask for donations.

889
00:36:52,460 --> 00:36:53,420
What do you think?

890
00:36:53,565 --> 00:36:54,434
Stop your pointless chatter.

891
00:36:56,325 --> 00:36:57,175
Fine.

892
00:36:58,020 --> 00:36:58,954
I'll think of something myself.

893
00:37:18,660 --> 00:37:20,500
Your lot

894
00:37:20,619 --> 00:37:24,779
is the best out of all.

895
00:37:25,299 --> 00:37:26,579
That's all?

896
00:37:28,700 --> 00:37:30,779
Is this a good thing or a bad thing?

897
00:37:30,779 --> 00:37:32,500
-I didn't get it.
-Yeah. Tell us the details.

898
00:37:32,660 --> 00:37:35,379
-Is it good or bad?
-Late bloomer.

899
00:37:36,420 --> 00:37:38,460
How late is late?

900
00:37:38,980 --> 00:37:44,339
According to how
modern people calculate age,

901
00:37:44,980 --> 00:37:47,139
it'll be around 60 years old.

902
00:37:50,099 --> 00:37:50,980
60 years old?

903
00:37:51,859 --> 00:37:53,139
That's pretty good.

904
00:37:53,379 --> 00:37:54,500
People always seek out

905
00:37:54,500 --> 00:37:55,940
senior TCM practitioners.

906
00:37:55,940 --> 00:37:56,770
That's not it.

907
00:37:56,859 --> 00:37:57,700
Both of my parents

908
00:37:57,819 --> 00:37:58,740
made a name for themselves

909
00:37:58,740 --> 00:37:59,819
at a young age.

910
00:37:59,819 --> 00:38:00,740
But I'm only making a name
for myself at 60?

911
00:38:00,740 --> 00:38:01,819
Do you think that's appropriate?

912
00:38:01,980 --> 00:38:03,099
Yeah.

913
00:38:03,099 --> 00:38:05,220
Why not? I think it's good enough
to make a name for yourself.

914
00:38:05,420 --> 00:38:06,539
Look at me.

915
00:38:06,539 --> 00:38:07,859
I'll stay like this
for the rest of my life.

916
00:38:08,100 --> 00:38:09,940
I'm the same even when I'm 80.

917
00:38:10,020 --> 00:38:11,059
Are you trying

918
00:38:11,477 --> 00:38:12,351
to console me?

919
00:38:15,260 --> 00:38:16,099
I don't think so.

920
00:38:19,660 --> 00:38:21,500
Let's check out the other stalls.

921
00:38:21,700 --> 00:38:22,560
Alright.

922
00:38:22,884 --> 00:38:24,323
-Let's check them out.
-They're selling food.

923
00:38:24,836 --> 00:38:25,916
-Meng Meng, let's go.
-Let's go.

924
00:38:26,077 --> 00:38:26,935
Let's go.

925
00:38:35,700 --> 00:38:36,613
Excuse me.

926
00:38:37,260 --> 00:38:38,059
Let me ask you something.

927
00:38:38,859 --> 00:38:40,900
Are you a human or a robot?

928
00:38:41,500 --> 00:38:45,020
Sir, what other questions do you have?

929
00:38:45,932 --> 00:38:47,412
It's fine. Thank you.

930
00:38:52,779 --> 00:38:53,660
One of them

931
00:38:53,899 --> 00:38:55,139
is a late bloomer

932
00:38:55,339 --> 00:38:56,500
while the other one is a prodigy.

933
00:39:06,619 --> 00:39:08,020
What should we do now?

934
00:39:08,779 --> 00:39:09,819
I just feel apologetic

935
00:39:10,099 --> 00:39:11,619
toward Ms Dong.

936
00:39:12,099 --> 00:39:14,619
You always led a reclusive life.

937
00:39:15,020 --> 00:39:15,879
Now,

938
00:39:16,588 --> 00:39:17,908
you're here.

939
00:39:18,220 --> 00:39:20,339
But we don't even have a classroom
for you to teach them.

940
00:39:20,379 --> 00:39:21,859
Yeah, it's all my fault.

941
00:39:22,660 --> 00:39:24,020
I should've expected this to happen

942
00:39:24,220 --> 00:39:25,260
when I severed my ties

943
00:39:25,260 --> 00:39:26,900
with them.

944
00:39:27,460 --> 00:39:28,420
Actually, they're not obliged

945
00:39:28,692 --> 00:39:29,972
to help us out

946
00:39:30,148 --> 00:39:31,628
for free.

947
00:39:32,085 --> 00:39:33,204
Businessmen

948
00:39:33,707 --> 00:39:35,788
value profit over righteousness.

949
00:39:36,844 --> 00:39:37,844
That's a hasty generalization.

950
00:39:39,980 --> 00:39:42,299
There are many
righteous businessmen too.

951
00:39:43,980 --> 00:39:44,861
Master,

952
00:39:45,235 --> 00:39:46,836
you always told me

953
00:39:47,099 --> 00:39:48,500
that if I have an idea,

954
00:39:48,619 --> 00:39:49,859
everything will fall into place.

955
00:39:50,139 --> 00:39:51,059
I had this idea

956
00:39:51,660 --> 00:39:52,700
for a long time.

957
00:39:52,980 --> 00:39:54,180
Why isn't anyone

958
00:39:54,180 --> 00:39:55,740
giving me a classroom?

959
00:39:56,220 --> 00:39:57,539
You see,

960
00:39:57,539 --> 00:39:58,900
that only works

961
00:39:59,260 --> 00:40:00,260
when you're Buddha.

962
00:40:01,420 --> 00:40:02,339
You still have a long way to go.

963
00:40:02,339 --> 00:40:03,220
You're right.

964
00:40:04,660 --> 00:40:05,740
You see,

965
00:40:06,267 --> 00:40:07,668
knowledge and action
should go hand in hand.

966
00:40:08,500 --> 00:40:10,819
From realising
the righteousness of the event

967
00:40:11,059 --> 00:40:12,660
to the completion of the event,

968
00:40:12,660 --> 00:40:13,573
everything else in between

969
00:40:13,779 --> 00:40:15,299
acts as your trial.

970
00:40:16,700 --> 00:40:19,180
God is giving you an ordeal

971
00:40:19,420 --> 00:40:21,180
called The Dignity Ordeal.

972
00:40:23,660 --> 00:40:24,700
Master, you're right.

973
00:40:26,700 --> 00:40:28,500
Master, I'll be honest with you.

974
00:40:28,500 --> 00:40:30,339
In the past, I didn't think

975
00:40:31,059 --> 00:40:32,339
that this industry was that tough.

976
00:40:33,059 --> 00:40:34,260
But now, it's...

977
00:40:36,579 --> 00:40:37,500
Think about it.

978
00:40:38,460 --> 00:40:39,940
Throughout your career,

979
00:40:40,740 --> 00:40:41,740
you were talented

980
00:40:42,460 --> 00:40:44,139
and you had academic qualifications.

981
00:40:44,139 --> 00:40:44,988
And,

982
00:40:45,299 --> 00:40:46,900
you had elders like us

983
00:40:46,900 --> 00:40:48,020
backing you up.

984
00:40:48,420 --> 00:40:50,379
Of course you had a smooth journey.

985
00:40:50,539 --> 00:40:51,407
You're right.

986
00:40:51,579 --> 00:40:52,539
Now,

987
00:40:52,740 --> 00:40:55,020
I'm old.

988
00:40:55,500 --> 00:40:57,420
I'm afraid I won't be able
to back you up anymore.

989
00:40:57,900 --> 00:40:59,180
I'm afraid you need to back me up

990
00:41:00,020 --> 00:41:02,180
in the future.

991
00:41:03,500 --> 00:41:05,900
Dad, such chatter is meaningless.

992
00:41:06,579 --> 00:41:08,059
Now, we need to figure out a way

993
00:41:08,059 --> 00:41:09,460
to resolve this issue.

994
00:41:09,740 --> 00:41:10,700
Yeah.

995
00:41:13,260 --> 00:41:14,180
Ms Dong,

996
00:41:14,180 --> 00:41:15,500
I'm truly sorry.

997
00:41:15,500 --> 00:41:17,500
We invited you all the way here,

998
00:41:17,740 --> 00:41:18,610
however,

999
00:41:18,900 --> 00:41:20,500
we don't even have a place

1000
00:41:20,500 --> 00:41:21,700
for you to teach them.

1001
00:41:21,980 --> 00:41:22,819
That's fine.

1002
00:41:24,460 --> 00:41:25,460
When we decide

1003
00:41:26,740 --> 00:41:28,460
to take the righteous path,

1004
00:41:29,059 --> 00:41:30,379
we have to put in much more effort

1005
00:41:30,539 --> 00:41:32,779
than taking the back door.

1006
00:41:33,660 --> 00:41:34,819
God will test you

1007
00:41:34,819 --> 00:41:36,020
repeatedly

1008
00:41:36,740 --> 00:41:38,020
to see

1009
00:41:38,900 --> 00:41:40,779
whether you're truly sincere
in taking this path.

1010
00:41:42,651 --> 00:41:43,559
If you can pass God's test

1011
00:41:44,059 --> 00:41:45,619
every time without changing your goal,

1012
00:41:46,180 --> 00:41:48,059
you'll achieve what you wish for.

1013
00:41:50,700 --> 00:41:51,660
In my opinion,

1014
00:41:52,059 --> 00:41:53,059
this isn't even

1015
00:41:53,339 --> 00:41:54,779
an ordeal for you.

1016
00:41:55,779 --> 00:41:56,674
You're

1017
00:41:56,779 --> 00:41:58,059
an academician.

1018
00:41:58,460 --> 00:42:00,579
You published books and
made a name for yourself.

1019
00:42:02,099 --> 00:42:03,339
But people like us?

1020
00:42:03,859 --> 00:42:04,900
It's quite difficult for us

1021
00:42:05,819 --> 00:42:07,700
to pass our legacy
to the next generation.

1022
00:42:09,059 --> 00:42:10,420
In Taoism,

1023
00:42:10,700 --> 00:42:11,900
masters will look for
their own disciples.

1024
00:42:12,819 --> 00:42:14,500
I agreed to join your class

1025
00:42:15,020 --> 00:42:16,500
not because to help you out.

1026
00:42:17,059 --> 00:42:18,579
I'm helping myself out.

1027
00:42:19,524 --> 00:42:20,406
I was thinking

1028
00:42:20,652 --> 00:42:21,652
that I'll encounter a disciple

1029
00:42:22,109 --> 00:42:24,268
who's a kindred spirit
if I teach enough classes.

1030
00:42:25,299 --> 00:42:26,619
Maybe that person is willing
to inherit our legacy

1031
00:42:27,779 --> 00:42:30,139
without changing anything.

1032
00:42:33,580 --> 00:42:34,713
(The prescriptions and remedies
used in this drama)

1033
00:42:34,801 --> 00:42:36,316
(are referenced from relevant
traditional Chinese medicine books)

1034
00:42:36,420 --> 00:42:38,134
(Do not use without medical advice)
